---
title: Sausage Banh-Mi with Cucumber and Carrot Pickle and Wedges
description: We love good Sausage Banh-Mi and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sausage-banh-mi-d33a10ca-cc190164.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/sausage-banh-mi-5f05cf8bc0902c28ff5639eb-c69f413f.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/sausage-banh-mi-5f05cf8bc0902c28ff5639eb
author: Mimi Morley
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Thai
nutrition:
  calories: 814 kcal
  fat: 39 g
  saturated fat: 13 g
  carbohydrates: 91 g
  sugar: 11 g
  protein: 30 g
  sodium: 2.4 g
  serving size: 618
